  "testimonials": [
    {
      "quote": "I first came to look at the village with a friend about six years ago. It was in its early development stage. Being a builder, I looked at the plans and was suitably impressed and realised that moving to Highfield Country Estate would be ideal for my wife and myself.",
      "author": "David & Shona Hollinshead"
    },
    {
      "quote": "I moved to T A to be closer to my family who all live in the surrounding area. I love my villa especially in the way I can potter in my own garden and veggie garden. I also enjoy sharing my home with visitors to the village. The garden team, office team and directors are like family. I feel very well looked after here",
      "author": "Colleen Logan"
    },
    {
      "quote": "After living a lifetime on the open country on a lifestyle block we had a lot of soul searching to do when our chance came to move to Highfield. From the start of moving out throughout the time we have been here, our thanks to everyone + staff for a smooth move. They were all very helpful and they made us feel very welcome.\n\nThere is so much one can do, e.g. Bowls, cards, evening socials, etc. A real fun time had by all. Our family are happy that we are so settled and enjoying our life at a slower pace.",
      "author": "Frances and Les Mosen."
    }
  ],
  "news": [
    {
      "category": "Awards",
      "title": "Finalist Again in 2025 NZ's Best Awards",
      "date": "January 2025",
      "image": "https://rocketspark.pictures/CF-a0fada1e-2b29-4f26-a1e4-b51cb29b3406/fit=cover,gravity=auto,width=1600,height=900,sharpen=1.00/17904c80bee8ea301909bb1b33410ad9.jpg",
      "paragraphs": [
        "We are proud to announce that Highfield Country Estate has once again been named a Finalist in the Best Medium/Large Retirement & Lifestyle Village – North Island category at the NZ's Best Awards. This marks our seventh consecutive year of recognition, following our 2020 win.",
        "A huge thank you to our incredible team and wonderful residents who make Highfield the special place it is."
      ]
    },
    {
      "category": "Events",
      "title": "Annual Spring Garden Festival a Blooming Success",
      "date": "October 2024",
      "image": "https://rocketspark.pictures/CF-a0fada21-38b5-4422-8904-c9c498edcbc9/fit=cover,gravity=auto,width=1600,height=900,sharpen=1.00/1a5025eb36b0789d0f4267bba2011afb.jpg",
      "paragraphs": [
        "Our annual Spring Garden Festival was a wonderful celebration of colour and community. Residents and visitors enjoyed guided garden tours, a plant swap, morning tea, and a floral arrangement demonstration by our talented garden team led by Jackie Cosgrove.",
        "The festival highlighted the incredible work our gardening team puts into maintaining Highfield's beautiful nine-and-a-half hectares of grounds."
      ]
    },
    {
      "category": "Development",
      "title": "New Stage of Villas Now Under Construction",
      "date": "August 2024",
      "image": "https://rocketspark.pictures/CF-a0fada23-c4d1-42cc-8fb0-dce01296a823/fit=cover,gravity=auto,width=1600,height=900,sharpen=1.00/edc7ed4045e20cb7578a1e4f7e120535.jpg",
      "paragraphs": [
        "Exciting times at Highfield as construction has commenced on our newest stage of villas. Under the expert guidance of Project Manager Todd Kerr, these new homes will feature our latest designs with modern kitchens, spacious living areas, and beautiful outdoor terraces.",
        "Interested in securing one of these brand-new villas? Get in touch with us today."
      ]
    },
    {
      "category": "Community",
      "title": "A Celebration of Talent at Highfield",
      "date": "June 2024",
      "image": "https://rocketspark.pictures/CF-a0fada0f-7cd4-4a96-bf9b-73ec9980b695/fit=cover,gravity=auto,width=800,height=600,sharpen=1.00/20404246214e021835e472f6e83f91e9.jpg",
      "paragraphs": [
        "Our residents showcased their incredible talents at a special community event, featuring watercolour painting, woodwork, pottery, and even live musical performances. The evening was a true testament to the vibrant and creative spirit of the Highfield community.",
        "At Highfield, we believe in celebrating the unique gifts each resident brings to our village family."
      ]
    }
  ],
